{"tid":628049,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[讀書App] 召集所有句子迷/鐘意睇書既巴絲打 寫句子送Kindle閱讀器","createTime":"2018-04-13T12:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T15:31:45.000Z","uid":104580,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ca69c8252593c23347f8dab4db9539e91da8ba10","tid":628049,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打睇左好多書,然後好快唔記得晒?<br />\n<br />\n又或者睇完本書都唔明白當中既內容?<br />\n<br />\n有見及此, 小弟係工餘時間同朋友寫左一個 讀書工具既app出黎 名叫【圍讀】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係希望讀書唔再孤單,可以透過圍讀平台去分享自己對書睇法,記錄自己鐘意既句子<br />\n<br />\n鐘意睇書既你,不妨花少少時間去嘗試下呢個平台, 記錄留俾手機與電腦，思考留俾大腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n功能介紹<br />\n- 寫下書評、讀後感、筆記<br />\n- 製造書單 收藏不同種類書本<br />\n- 摘下精彩句子<br />\n- 記錄完成閱讀的日期，讀過的書一目了然<br />\n- 查看好友的閱讀記錄<br />\n- 快速連結至圖書館、書店等網頁[製作中]<br />\n<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://weido.com.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweido.com.tw&d=NLRT3BKytKoMD2lY%2F%2BqSXtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=23449b7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://weido.com.tw</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.weido\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.weido&d=NLRT3BKytKoMD2lY%2F%2BqSXtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=e07d795b\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.weido</a><br />\n<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1353032466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1353032466&d=NLRT3BKytKoMD2lY%2F%2BqSXtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=260832ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1353032466</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/weido.read/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fweido.read%2F&d=NLRT3BKytKoMD2lY%2F%2BqSXtWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=95786914\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/weido.read/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意睇書既你,又想知道下每本書既精華,不妨Like 我地既facebook page, 每日都有唔同既書評推薦<br />\n<br />\n句子首頁<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/13/LFgXdU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2FLFgXdU.png&h=27b7c3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可愛成就頭像<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/13/2zGCZy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F2zGCZy.png&h=677e51d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n書評界面<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/13/6wzlVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F6wzlVn.png&h=f48aafcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e3ad65a336e600f69aaf8da121120b055f58874","tid":628049,"uid":104580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意睇書既巴絲打，都可以去google play／app store 幫我留個好評<br />\n<br />\n當可憐一下IT狗既辛酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9fb321020410002a146026802289685669263b","tid":628049,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f02eec218eb3d92122715a5f9a64caec9bf342c","tid":628049,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4f2d367f8f6c18f177ecc573d69dfd479cdc09","tid":628049,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774bce9634895479b933840d646b99c2fc572d8e","tid":628049,"uid":42175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T